ai-mil7.5.2:2.1_0: Furthermore, great king, he seeks out a seat that is proper for himself.
ai-mil7.5.2:2.2_0: In the same way, one who has the five constituents (of mind and body) that provides fuel for attachment, such is the origin of form, such is the ending of feeling. Such is the origin of perception, such is the ending of form, feeling, perception, choices, or consciousness?’
